  "dateModified": "2026-04-27",
  "datePublished": "2026-04-27",
  "description": "The school presupposes a material claim about declining net energy that lives in the EROEI literature outside cybernetic postliberalism proper. Useful-stage global fossil-fuel EROEI is now ~3.5:1, below Hall's 5:1 floor for complex society; the substrate's contraction is what made the apparatus's redistribution onto bodies and platforms structurally necessary.",
  "name": "The Energetic Substrate",
